spec_data.Name: soci-sqlite3-devel
spec_data.Description:
This package contains the SQLite3 back-end for soci, i.e., header
files and dynamic libraries specific to the SQLite3 database. If you
would like to develop programs using soci and SQLite3, you will need
to install soci-sqlite3.
